Dialogue: 1,0:23:45.15,0:23:50.16,ED2-JP,,0,0,0,,夢のはじまりの合図が鳴る
Comment: 1,0:22:30.66,0:22:34.12,ED2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,480)}I’ll always believe tomorrow
